  "general_provisions": "This bill modifies provisions related to student information systems for local education agencies.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>requires the State Board of Education to procure a statewide student information system;<hr><ltbullet>allows a local education agency to maintain the agency's own student information system under certain conditions;<hr><ltbullet>establishes requirements for local education agency-maintained systems;<hr><ltbullet>establishes enforcement provisions for noncompliance;<hr><ltbullet>requires audits of certain local education agencies;<hr><ltbullet>establishes implementation timelines; and<hr><ltbullet>makes conforming changes.",
